<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.6">
<l>taḷḷit taḷirnaṭai yiṭṭiḷam piḷḷaiyāy</l>
<l>uḷḷatti ṉuḷḷē yavaḷai yuṟanōkki</l>
<l>kaḷḷatti ṉālvanta pēycci mulaiyuyir</l>
<l>tuḷḷac cuvaittāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">tuvakkaṟa vuṇṭāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As a young boy, with a fitful, staggering gait,</l>
<l>seeing that which dwelt in her heart of hearts,</l>
<l>he sucked the drop of life from the breast</l>
<l rend="Indent">of the demoness who came through deception,</l>
<l>Because of him, now we’re at our end.</l>
<l>Because of he who was fully bound,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
